claim.claim-text:
A battery pack comprising:
a housing;
a terminal block;
a printed circuit board electrically connected to the terminal block;
at least one battery cell; and,
the terminal block supporting a plurality of terminals, each of said plurality of terminals having a first end for connecting to an electric device, a second end for connecting to the printed circuit board and a bent portion, occurring between the first and second ends, that provides each of the terminals with limited flexible movement.

A battery pack comprising:
a housing having a base portion connected to a tower portion;
a terminal block in the tower portion of the housing;
at least one printed circuit board in the tower portion and electrically connected to the terminal block; and,
at least one battery cell in the base portion.

An electrical combination, comprising:
a power tool having a motor and a plurality of tool terminals;
a battery charger having a plurality of charger terminals;
a battery pack including a housing, a terminal block with a plurality of terminals, and at least one printed circuit board electrically connected to the terminal block and, at least one battery cell, said battery pack further including a mechanical lock out associated with at least one of said plurality of terminals for identifying the battery pack prior to engagement with either of the power tool or battery charger.
